description:
This document is aimed at developing the protocol for the economic evaluation of the GerOnTe intervention. This report corresponds to the deliverable D3.2, that is part of work-package 3 &ldquo;Developing the methods for Geronte&rdquo; which supports GERONTE Objective 3.3 &ldquo;Develop a model to perform economic evaluation of complex healthcare services&rdquo;, Objective 4 &ldquo;Demonstrate in 16 study sites from three EU Countries the feasibility and effectiveness of the GerOnTe model&rdquo; and Objective 5.3 &ldquo;Perform economic evaluation of complex healthcare services, using the model developed under O3 and the data gathered under O4&rdquo;.. 
 This protocol illustrates the methods that will be used to conduct the economic evaluation of the GERONTE model in France, Belgium, and the Netherlands. 
 Version 2 - is the updated version of the protocol&nbsp;

